tifamily lending and investment in  and as senior vice president in charge of its american communities fund since  he served as a director of the office of securitization of the resolution trust corporation he spent eight years on wall street with kidder peabody  co and morgan stanley  co as an officer where his focus was mortgage finance and related products mr bacon has been independent director of comcast corporation since november  and served as its lead independent director he has been independent directorof ally financial inc since february   he serves as a director of bentall kennedy management us limited partnership he has been director of comcast holdings corp since november  he has been an independent director of welltower inc since february  he has been an independent director of forest city realty trust inc since december   he serves as a member of the board of trustees for stanford university he served as a director for fannie mae foundation he served as a director of national equity fund inc mr bacon is awarded the order of the british empire for his contributions to the marshall scholars program he holds master of business administration from the harvard graduate school of business master of science in international relations from the london school of economics and bachelor of arts from stanford universityread full background corporate headquarters bethesda maryland united statesphone fax  board members memberships directorbentall kennedy management us limited partnershippresentindependent directorcomcast corporationpresentdirectorcomcast holdings corppresentindependent directorforest city realty trust incpresentindependent directorally financial incpresentindependent directorwelltower inc education ba stanford universitymba harvard business schoolms the london school of economics and political science other affiliations comcast corporationstanford universityfederal national mortgage associationforest city realty trust incwelltower incally financial i